The soft foam padding adds an extra layer of protection while maintaining a modern look. I appreciate the versatility to mount it on the wall, furniture, or even the ceiling, offering flexibility in placement.This mount not only clears up precious surface space but also keeps the entertainment area organized. The black color complements the Fire TV Cube's design, creating a seamless integration with my home decor.The Metal Wall Mount for Fire TV Cube is a fantastic addition for those seeking a space-saving, secure, and visually appealing solution for their Fire TV Cube. It's a small investment with significant returns in both functionality and aesthetics.
